data.description: Tucked away in South East Boise's Painted Ridge subdivision, this 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath has the garage you didn't know you need. Currently set up with a gym area behind the RV bay and still plenty of storage for your hobbies and toys in the back of the 2 car garage bay! Open concept floor plan that makes hosting effortless with the half bath on the main floor, large butlers pantry off the beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances and gas stove plus the covered patio for BBQs this summer. Main floor bedroom (currently used as an office) has a secret closet! Upstairs includes the conveniently located laundry room, 3 large bedrooms and the luxurious owners suite. Icing on the cake is the OWNED solar panels giving you an extremely low Idaho Power bill. Community offers in-ground pool with changing rooms and grass open space. This lively neighborhood is just minutes to Micron, Boise Airport, Simplot Sports Complex and I-84 for your easy commute to Downtown Boise, the mountains and beyond.
